            <p id="How_did_we_keep_romance_in_the_marriage_Well_that_was_easy_for">
            How did we keep romance in the marriage? Well that was easy for me because she was such a beautiful, gorgeous woman. It wasn’t hard for me at all, because it just came naturally. <br /><br />We definitely loved being parents, and we enjoyed being around our kids. I don’t know if it had much to do with us, but I think we had children sent to us from Heavenly Father that were good to begin with. <a name="x"></a> We taught them at an early age to be good people and it stuck. In a nutshell that’s kind of how it all came to be. It’s hard to put your finger on any one thing, we were just very blessed. <br />
            </p>

